narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: French 120 is a lot of work, but it is a worthwhile course to take if your goal is to actually learn French.

This class is a continuation of French 110. If you take this class you will be doing many of the same things as you did in French 110 - learning basic vocab and grammar, taking weekly tests, and following a video/story to learn the lessons.
French 120 is an excellent course for either those who want a good grasp of the french language or those who intend to become fluent in it.
Great course! Take it! It's well-paced and instructors are very understanding and personable.
Yes, I would definitely recommend French 120 but only if the student is truly invested in learning the language because otherwise you will fall behind on the work.
